          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2495Step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop the <strong>chives</strong> finely</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>chopped chives</strong> and <strong>garlic</strong> to a bowl along with the<strong> mayo </strong>and a splash of <strong>cold water </strong>and give everything a good mix up<strong> </strong>– this is your<strong> chive mayo</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>chipotle paste</strong> to a bowl with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>chipotle dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
